name: Simplicity
description:
A piece made with basic shapes which are then cut into inorganic shapes which later is repeated with a brick based grid. The title is kept as "Simplicity" as it's completely made up of basic shapes with a small touch of wires, upon zooming in, you'll find smaller patterns within the shapes which are the wires mentioned above. This whole piece is made in 2d space.

Technical Specifications 
Dimensions used - 6000 * 6000 pixels
Pattern Structure - Brick
Exported Image - PNG
